Hello everyone,


The French Embassy is hosting an *Education Fair on October 1st, 2016 in
Chennai with 30 French Institutions participating in this event* (registrat=
ion
link mentioned below). This is a unique opportunity where students will be
able to have a one on one interaction with some of the best Management and
Engineering Schools in France.



For this purpose, officials from French Embassy are coming down to our
institute to do a small presentation on study opportunities in France which
would also include a fun quiz for the students on France as well as will
promote the fair. Details of the session are as follows:


*Date:* Sept 20th
*Time:* 5:30 to 6:30 pm
*Venue:* IC&SR Hall 2


Details of Education Fair are available at the link below:

